# Production build config (committed on purpose).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* are inlined into the client bundle at build time. These are the
# PUBLIC Supabase values for the live project (anon key is public by design and
# protected by RLS — it already ships to every browser). Committing them here
# makes the production build connect to real Supabase regardless of Vercel
# dashboard env-var scoping. Vercel dashboard env vars, if set, still override.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://mtldmawenkdebtchnocs.supabase.co
